Project description

BioBlend is a Python library for interacting with the Galaxy API.

BioBlend is supported and tested on:

  • Python 3.7 - 3.11

  • Galaxy release 19.05 and later.

Full docs are available at https://bioblend.readthedocs.io/ with a quick libraryoverview also available in ABOUT.rst.
